ssa (  d. <i>c.</i>395 ), Gregory of Tours (  538–94 ), and  Pope Gregory the Great  (  <i>c.</i>540–604 ). A famous bearer of the name in modern times is the film star  Gregory Peck  (  1916–2003 ). The name has traditionally been popular in Scotland, where it is often found in the form  <b>Gregor</b> ."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Gregory Rokesley was born about 1235. He had at least 1 son."},"et":{"Abt 1235–":"umbes 1235–Surnud","1250–1332":"1250–1332","1235–Male":"1235–Surnud","1235":"1235","1332":"1332","Abt 1235":"umbes 1235","1250":"1250"},"fi":{"Abt 1235–":"noin 1235–Kuollut","1250–1332":"1250–1332","1235–Male":"1235–Kuollut","1235":"1235","1332":"1332","Abt 1235":"noin 1235","1250":"1250"},"fr":{"Abt 1235–":"environ 1235–Décédé","1250–1332":"1250–1332","1235–Male":"1235–Décédé","1235":"1235","1332":"1332","Abt 1235":"environ 1235","1250":"1250","lifeSummary":"Gregory Rokesley est né environ 1235. Il a eu au moins 1 fils."},"de":{"Abt 1235–":"um 1235–Verstorben","1250–1332":"1250–1332","1235–Male":"1235–Verstorben","1235":"1235","1332":"1332","Abt 1235":"um 1235","1250":"1250","lifeSummary":"Gregory Rokesley wurde um 1235 geboren. Er hatte mindestens 1 Sohn."},"ht":{"Abt 1235–":"about 1235–Desede","1250–1332":"1250–1332","1235–Male":"1235–Desede","1235":"1235","1332":"1332","Abt 1235":"about 1235","1250":"1250"},"hu":{"Abt 1235–":"1235 körül–elhunyt","1250–1332":"1250–1332","1235–Male":"1235–elhunyt","1235":"1235","1332":"1332","Abt 1235":"1235 körül","1250":"1250"},"id":{"Abt 1235–":"sekitar 1235–Telah Meninggal","1250–1332":"1250–1332","1235–Male":"1235–Telah Meninggal","1235":"1235","1332":"1332","Abt 1235":"sekitar 1235","1250":"1250"},"it":{"Abt 1235–":"circa 1235–Deceduto","1250–1332":"1250–1332","1235–Male":"1235–Deceduto","1235":"1235","1332":"1332","Abt 1235":"circa 1235","1250":"1250","lifeSummary":"Gregory Rokesley è nato il circa 1235. Lui avuto almeno 1 figlio."},"ja":{"Abt 1235–":"約1235年–死亡","1250–1332":"1250年–1332年","1235–Male":"1235年–死亡",